Package: mbtazone
Title: Implements the MBTA Communities Compliance Model in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Fernando", "Hidalgo", , "dhidalgo@mit.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the Massachusetts MBTA Communities Act compliance
    model in R, providing automated zoning compliance assessment tools.
    Replaces manual Excel-based workflows with robust calculation functions
    for housing unit capacity and interactive planning capabilities.
